'''Karl Heinrich Marx''', illul deg 5 si [[Magu]] deg ussegwas 1818 di tmurt n [[Trier]] illan di Rheinland tamurt n [[Lalman]] yemmut di 14 di [[Meɣres]] 1883 di temdint n [[London]]. Marx illa d argaz n tsertit u d-amesnagay ameqṛan, d netta id isnulfan ayen i wumi neqqar [[Tazdukla]] "le communisme", id yeqaren belli ulac amgarad ger imdanen ɣas ulamma yella deg ixeddim nsen n yal ass.

==Tudert-is==
Ilul Karl Heinrich Marx di Trier asegwas n 1818. Yella d wis sin ger 8 Tam watmaten-is. Vava-s, Heinrich Marx (1782–1838), d-abugaṭu, yefrurid deg yiwet twacult twudayt Ackenaz. Jed-nsen Meier Halevi Marx yella dawday, m-ad mmi-s d warraw n mmi-s uɣalen d-imasiḥiyen, ẓẓiẓrgen isem nsen ɣer Heinrich iwakken ad izmiren ad xedmen, yemma-s n Karl, Henriette Pressburg (20 [[Yulyu]] 1788-30 [[Wamber]] 1863), d tawdayt n [[Timura n Wadda|tmura n wadda]].

